{"type": "article", "id": 30051, "title": "混凝土托盘", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-24T22:51:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160724220121kaTq84n7Svrf2ysJ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.laselvastudio.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LaSelva</a> 工作室最近与 Iván Zúñiga 共同为墨西哥公司 Más 打造了一组名为 <a href=\"http://www.laselvastudio.es/#!flota/c245e\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flota</a> 的托盘系列，两种材质的搭配缓和了混凝土制品容易给人带来的冰冷感，加入了一丝柔和的气质。木质底座的存在以及随处可见的弧度软化了混凝土固有的坚硬感，使这些造型各异的托盘能够很好地融入居家环境当中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724220143vxt2usjCclDeLUOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724220143SjZUCK7pyiWQt0a8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639810\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724220143M80A43maDSu6b7xX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724220143C6GSOqhcHoF2J73E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.038591\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}